@startuml
hide methods
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

' Version de travail pour la V2.
' Elle reprend la V1 et sera enrichie au fil des arbitrages.

class User {
  +id: UUID
  +email: string
  +passwordHash: string
  +displayName: string
  +systemRole: USER|ADMIN
  +createdAt: datetime
}

class Universe {
  +id: UUID
  +name: string
  +description: text
  +createdAt: datetime
}

class CharacterProfile {
  +id: UUID
  +name: string
  +portraitUrl: string
  +personality: text
  +createdAt: datetime
}

class Campaign {
  +id: UUID
  +name: string
  +invitationCode: string
  +status: DRAFT|LOBBY|ACTIVE|PAUSED|ENDED
  +createdAt: datetime
}

class Session {
  +id: UUID
  +title: string
  +status: PLANNED|ACTIVE|CLOSED
}

class Character {
  +id: UUID
  +type: PLAYER|NPC|ENEMY
  +level: int
  +experience: int
  +strength: int
  +agility: int
  +intelligence: int
  +charisma: int
  +endurance: int
  +luck: int
  +currentHp: int
  +maxHp: int
  +currentMana: int
  +maxMana: int
}

class Event {
  +id: UUID
  +type: NARRATIVE|COMBAT|SYSTEM
  +title: string
  +createdAt: datetime
}

User "1" -- "0..*" CharacterProfile
Universe "1" -- "0..*" CharacterProfile
Universe "1" -- "0..*" Campaign
Campaign "1" -- "0..*" Session
Campaign "1" -- "0..*" Character
CharacterProfile "0..1" -- "0..*" Character
Session "1" -- "0..*" Event

note bottom of Event
V2 accueillera les raffinements :
- historique
- audit
- consequences
- notifications
- progression detaillee
end note
@enduml
